description: Nord Insuretech Group AB engages in the provision of financial technology services. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2020-02-14. The Company’s business concept is to deliver insurance products to partners using an adaptable digital platform. Nord Insuretech Group’s digital platform consists of three main components: Core insurance system, Robot solution for onboarding customers and Data and analysis platform. The firm operates in Nordic region.
name: Nord Insuretech Group AB
